ENTRY            M0195   20260107   20260226   20260226       M143
SUBENT        M0195001   20260107   20260226   20260226       M143
BIB                 12         29
TITLE      Photofission cross section of Ra-226
AUTHOR     (E.A.Zhagrov,Yu.A.Nemilov,N.V.Nikitina,Yu.A.Selitskiy)
INSTITUTE  (4RUSLEB)
REFERENCE  (J,SNP,13,537,1971)
            English translation of YF,13,934,1971.
FACILITY   (SYNCH,4RUSLEB)
SAMPLE     Two radium targets weighing 2140+-10 and 374 +-18 ug,
           which had been prepared by vacuum deposition; their
           diameter was 9 mm.
INC-SOURCE (BRST)
METHOD     (EXTB,SITA)
DETECTOR   (GLASD)
           (IOCH) The bremsstrahlung flux was measured with a
           thick-walled aluminum ionization chamber.
ERR-ANALYS (ERR-SYS) Systematic error includes:
           (ERR-1) Uncertainty in the target weight
           (ERR-2) Uncertainty in the fission registration
            efficiency
           (ERR-3) Uncertainty in the bremsstrahlung dosimetry
STATUS     (CURVE,,E.A.Zhagrov+,J,SNP,13,537,1971)
            Data from Fig. 3.
HISTORY    (19870807C)
           (19910202A) Corrected by V.Varlamov, V.Mclane
           (20121103A) SD: Updated to new date formats,lower case.
           Corrected according to the last EXFOR rules and Dict.
                Ref. on transl. was added.
                VV: REACTION code in SUBENT 002 was corrected.
           (20260107A) Corrected by VV and SD: REFERENCE,
            PART-DET, STATUS.
